OL,3,CFamilies claim 'smear campaign'
OL,4,Cagainst senior Guernsey politician
OL,6,FFamilies say the debate held to
OL,7,Fsuspend Guernsey's Deputy Chief
OL,8,FMinister was a "smear campaign being
OL,9,Fmounted against someone challenging
OL,10,Fmedical and health services".
OL,12,FThe debate saw Deputy St Pier avoid
OL,13,Fsuspension after breaking the States'
OL,14,FCode of Conduct for talking with a
OL,15,Fnational newspaper reporter about
OL,16,Fissues surrounding Dr Sandie Bohin.
