OL,3,CFamilies claim 'smear campaign'
OL,4,Cagainst senior Guernsey politician
OL,6,FBefore the debate, 17 signatories from
OL,7,Fthe pressure group 'Families for
OL,8,FCultural Change' argued in an open
OL,9,Fletter that penalising Deputy Gavin St
OL,10,FPier for speaking to the journalist
OL,11,Fabout healthcare safeguarding concerns
OL,12,Fwould set a dangerous precedent.
OL,14,FThey raised serious allegations
OL,15,Fagainst the Medical Specialist Group
OL,16,Fand the level of care their children
OL,17,Freceived.
