OL,4,Cagainst senior Guernsey politician
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News anonymously, one
OL,7,Fparent said they felt "medically
OL,8,Fgaslit" and is highlighting their
OL,9,Fstory "out of desperation".
OL,11,FThe group said: "As families, we
OL,12,Fapproached Deputy St Pier as an
OL,13,Felected representative with the power
OL,14,Fto highlight this issue.
OL,16,F"We did so of our own volition and out
OL,17,Fof desperation. Our voices were
OL,18,Fsuppressed or silenced."
