OL,4,Cagainst senior Guernsey politician
OL,6,FThe anonymous parent added: "Our story
OL,7,Fshould have been quite straightforward
OL,8,Fbecause my baby was in utero (in the
OL,9,Fwomb) and she was diagnosed with a
OL,10,Fstructural heart anomaly.
OL,12,F"A very clear plan was set out that we
OL,13,Fwere to look out for symptoms.
OL,15,F"When my baby was three months old, we
OL,16,Fhighlighted and spoke at length about
OL,17,Fthese symptoms that had started to
OL,18,Fshow themselves."
