OL,4,Cagainst senior Guernsey politician
OL,6,FBut the family later learned that
OL,7,Fnotes suggested their baby was
OL,8,F"fantastic, with no symptoms at all".
OL,10,FThe parent continued: "Later on, I had
OL,11,Fallegations that I was difficult to
OL,12,Fdeal with because I was fighting for a
OL,13,Freferral.
OL,15,F"After a CT scan in Southampton, we
OL,16,Ffound that our daughter did have an
OL,17,Fissue with her heart. It was actually
OL,18,Fworse than we thought it would be.
OL,20,F"So in August of 2021, our daughter
OL,21,Fwas operated on in Southampton."
