OL,4,Cagainst senior Guernsey politician
OL,6,FHowever, the parent explains that
OL,7,Fwhilst returning to Guernsey, their
OL,8,Fchild's breathing worsened.
OL,10,FThe parent explained: "We felt very
OL,11,Fstrongly that the symptoms really just
OL,12,Fhadn't abated. So we reported that to
OL,13,FDr Sandie Bohin and she claimed, this
OL,14,Fwas in October, that all of our
OL,15,Fdaughter's symptoms were down to a
OL,16,Fcase of respiratory virus (RSV)."
OL,18,FHowever, the family did not believe
OL,19,Fthis and kept pushing for more answers.
