OL,4,Cagainst senior Guernsey politician
OL,6,FThe parent added: "I was so tired of
OL,7,Fbeing gaslit.
OL,9,F"Every time I would take her to the
OL,10,Fdoctor's or to A&E, I would be told
OL,11,Fshe had croup, maybe she had Covid. We
OL,12,Fwere sticking the swabs up her nose,
OL,13,Fand we knew this had nothing to do
OL,14,Fwith Covid."
OL,16,FThe family's worries were confirmed as
OL,17,Fit was eventually discovered that the
OL,18,Fbaby needed further surgery, following
OL,19,Fan earlier procedure.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/17
