OL,6,FThe parent said: "She was originally
OL,7,Fcut around her ribs, and they went in
OL,8,Fto the side, but this time they had to
OL,9,Fcut the front to do a full sternotomy,
OL,10,Fopen up her chest.
OL,12,F"You're so vulnerable. You've got a
OL,13,Ftiny child, and you know what you're
OL,14,Fsaying, and you've got somebody
OL,15,Fdoubting these symptoms."
