OL,3,CFamilies claim 'smear campaign'
OL,4,Cagainst senior Guernsey politician
OL,6,FAfter discovering they were correct
OL,7,Fabout their child's symptoms, the
OL,8,Fparents submitted a complaint to
OL,9,FGuernsey's Medical Specialist Group
OL,10,F(MSG), which employs Dr Bohin and it
OL,11,Fwas partially upheld.
OL,13,FITV News has put the parent's claims
OL,14,Fto the Medical Specialist Group and Dr
OL,15,FBohin, but both said they cannot
OL,16,Fcomment on individual cases.
