OL,4,Cagainst senior Guernsey politician
OL,6,FThe States' independent Commissioner
OL,7,Ffor Standards, Dr Melissa McCullough,
OL,8,Fsays independent reviews "have
OL,9,Fconsistently found no wrongdoing
OL,10,Frelated to Dr Bohin's clinical
OL,11,Fjudgement or her actions".
OL,13,FHowever, more widely, a Health and
OL,14,FSocial Care report published several
OL,15,Fyears ago found that there is a bias
OL,16,Fagainst families who are inclined to
OL,17,Fseek second opinions and alternative
OL,18,Fapproaches.
