OL,3,CFamilies claim 'smear campaign'
OL,4,Cagainst senior Guernsey politician
OL,6,FIn all, 30 parents have come forward
OL,7,Fto Deputy St Pier, but many say they
OL,8,Fhave not officially complained because
OL,9,Fthey are worried about future support
OL,10,Fon an island with no other health
OL,11,Fproviders.
OL,13,FSeven of the families ITV News has
OL,14,Fspoken to shared their concerns about
OL,15,Fthe complaint process itself, claiming
OL,16,Fit is not uniform for every case and
OL,17,Fsome are not addressed appropriately.
OL,19,FDr Steve Evans, Chair of the Medical
OL,20,FSpecialist Group, said this criticism
OL,21,Fis "unfair".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/17
