OL,6,FHe added: "We have a joint complaint
OL,7,Fpolicy with HSC (Health and Social
OL,8,FCare) and MSG, there's a robust
OL,9,Fprocess with deadlines, and there's a
OL,10,Fright of appeal if people are unhappy
OL,11,Fwith the outcome.
OL,13,F"I think in the cases where we've
OL,14,Freceived complaints, they've been
OL,15,Finvestigated thoroughly, appropriately
OL,16,Fand fairly.
