OL,6,F"I think the other thing you have to
OL,7,Fconsider is that if a patient
OL,8,Fapproaches a deputy or a third party
OL,9,For the media, they can share as many
OL,10,Fdetails as they want to, whereas as
OL,11,Fprofessionals we are duty-bound by a
OL,12,Fcode of confidentiality."
OL,14,FAll complaints are dealt with through
OL,15,Fthe MSG and HSC itself; an independent
OL,16,Fbody is only brought in if a complaint
OL,17,Fdecision is appealed after those same
OL,18,Forganisations decide there are grounds
OL,19,Ffor it.
