OL,6,FThe parent continued: "It's made me
OL,7,Fterrified by the thought that my
OL,8,Fchildren might end up in that system
OL,9,Fagain.
OL,11,F"We don't have any contact with any
OL,12,Fpaediatricians here.
OL,14,F"We only have contact with Great
OL,15,FOrmond Street. And we will do so until
OL,16,Fmy child is at least 18 and possibly
OL,17,Flonger."
OL,19,FDeputy St Pier said he feels a duty to
OL,20,Fvoice families' concerns.
