OL,4,Cagainst senior Guernsey politician
OL,6,FHe explained: "The most significant
OL,7,Fthing to me is the people I am seeking
OL,8,Fto represent, which is a largely
OL,9,Fgrowing number of families who have
OL,10,Fhad poor experiences of engaging with
OL,11,Fthe health care system and a feeling
OL,12,Fof not being listened to.
OL,14,F"They have nobody to represent their
OL,15,Finterest or point of view - that is
OL,16,Fthe most important part of this story
OL,17,Fthat keeps getting forgotten."
