OL,6,FHe added why he thinks people are
OL,7,Fscared to complain: "I mean it's easy
OL,8,Fto point fingers at individuals or at
OL,9,Findividual organisations, but we need
OL,10,Fto recognise that this is probably a
OL,11,Fdeep cultural and systemic issue."
OL,13,FWhen Deputy St Pier is asked whether
OL,14,Fhe believes the issue is continuing
OL,15,Fand if the organisation has learnt
OL,16,Ffrom what has happened, he responded:
OL,17,F"No it's not, it's very much ongoing.
